snippet.title: League of Empires Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play & Conquer in the First True MMO Real Time Strategy Game on Blockchain
Buy, Sell & Rent Lands:
Every player will need a land to start playing. Got an excess land? Sell it or rent it on the Marketplace.
Build & Sell Artilleries:There are 10 different types of artilleries. Build your own, use in battlefields or sell them on the Marketplace.
Form Alliances:United we stand, divided we fall. Forge powerful alliances with global players and grow faster!
PvP & PvE Modes:Test and train your skills in PvE modes. Once ready, shift to PvP modes & Leagues and earn even better rewards!

https://leagueofempires.io/
